Params: {3: 'After breaking the glass ceiling, Gray Raven members jump into the carriage, shocking the occupants inside.'}
{3: 'What greets you is not the cramped and suffocating compartment you were expectingâ€”'}
{3: 'The spacious and luxurious double-deck carriage has a series of paintings hung along its walls. Even the staircases linking the two stories are all made from high-quality wood.'}
{3: 'These people are still living a lavish lifestyle despite being on a train that was made to run away from disaster.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: '...Feels like the Golden Age is brought back alive...'}
{2: 'Noble Man', 3: 'Were they fighting above the train?'}
{3: 'A tall man, who appears to be the leader, quickly mutes the crowd with just one line.'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: 'I am Aston. Standing next to me is the leader of Akdilek Commercial Alliance, Jamilah.'}
{3: 'The graceful young girl standing next to him gives a slight nod. No one can see her expression as her face is covered by a white veil.'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: "I'd like to express our warmest welcome, Babylonia."}
